| Java            | `.java`                                 |
| C#              | `.cs`                                   |
| Dart            | `.dart`                                 |
| Kotlin          | `.kt`, `.kts`                           |
| Swift           | `.swift`                                |
| HCL / Terraform | `.tf`, `.hcl`                           |
